meta.prompt: A captivating image of a dark, eerie ballerina robot, imbued with a cosmic horror theme. The robot stands gracefully in a dramatic pose, its body illuminated by dim, otherworldly light, casting elongated shadows. Its intricate design combines steampunk and dark fantasy elements, with a worn, organic appearance to its skirt that evokes decay and surrealism. Surrounding the robot is a mysterious, mechanical background that adds to the haunting atmosphere. The combination of these elements creates a striking visual narrative of a haunting, otherworldly dancer, drawing the viewer into a world of enigmatic beauty and chilling wonder.
